ty **1/3** of being correct.\n- The other two doors collectively had probability **2/3** of containing the car, and the host only removes goat possibilities, concentrating that **2/3** onto the single remaining unopened door.\n\nThat’s why switching gives **2/3**, not **1/2**."},"sequence_number":606}

